    {
      "name": "Phase 3 — Multi-Turn Sessions",
      "description": "Multi-Turn Conversations (Tutorial Step 3).\n\nMaintains conversation context across multiple HTTP calls using AgentSession. Run requests in order 1 → 5.\n\n**The sessionId is automatically captured** from request 1 and used in requests 2–5.",
