              "path": ["api", "sessions"]
            },
            "description": "Creates a new `AgentSession` and returns its ID.\n\nThe test script automatically saves `sessionId` to the collection variable so subsequent requests use it.\n\nExpected response:\n```json\n{ \"sessionId\": \"3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6\" }\n```"
