    {
      "name": "Phase 4 — Memory & Persistence",
      "description": "Memory (Tutorial Step 4).\n\nThe `UserMemoryService` extracts structured facts from user messages:\n- `\"my name is X\"` → stores `user_name`\n- `\"I love X\"` / `\"I like X\"` → stores `user_hobby`\n\nOn every subsequent turn these facts are injected as a system message so the agent always addresses the user by name.\n\nRun requests in order 1 → 4.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. Create Session (Memory Test)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/sessions",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "sessions"]
            },
            "description": "Creates a fresh session. The sessionId is auto-saved to the collection variable."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 201 Created', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "var json = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('sessionId', json.sessionId);",
                  "console.log('sessionId captured for Phase 4:', json.sessionId);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "2. Introduce Yourself (Facts Are Extracted)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"message\": \"Hi! My name is Alice and I love hiking.\"\n}",
              "options": {
                "raw": {
                  "language": "json"
                }
              }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/sessions/{{sessionId}}/run",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "sessions", "{{sessionId}}", "run"]
            },
            "description": "After this request, `UserMemoryService` stores:\n```json\n{ \"user_name\": \"Alice\", \"user_hobby\": \"hiking\" }\n```\nVerify via the 'Inspect Stored Memory' request."
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 200 OK', function () {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "3. Unrelated Question (Agent Uses Your Name)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n    \"message\": \"What is 2 + 2?\"\n}",
              "options": {
